data.description: Open, flowing living area with spacious den and a gas fireplace*Large kitchen and pantry with a Breakfast room*Formal dining room currently being used as an office*Covered entry with a leaded glass door* Foyer that has a soaring ceiling to the second floor and a powder room for guests*Upstairs features four spacious bedrooms and two full baths*Laminate and tiled flooring throughout*Inside laundry room*Huge fenced back yard features two sheds with electricity*The large shed measures 16' by 10' and was built in 2021. It features a window unit and windows for natural lighting*Newer roof!!*Located in preferred Flood zone X*Just minutes from I-10 for an easy commute*Restaurants and Fremaux Town Center close by by for your convenience*Seller will pay up to $15,000 in closing cost and prepaid items if Buyer makes a full price offer and makes loan application with Seller's preferred lender.
